<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1411,1546]" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,634,1483,1509]" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">Distribution and published records.</emphasis>
As with the previous species, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Svihla" baseAuthorityYear="1983" box="[991,1146,1483,1510]" class="Insecta" family="Oedemeridae" genus="Alloxantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="426" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="platytarsia">
<emphasis box="[991,1008,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1025,1146,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">platytarsia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Svihla, V." pageId="5" pageNumber="426" pagination="107 - 132" refId="ref6781" refString="Svihla, V. (1983) Results of the Czechoslovak-Iranian entomological expeditions to Iran 1970, 1973, and 1977. Coleoptera, Oedemeridae. Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae, 41, 107 - 132." type="journal article" year="1983">Švihla (1983)</bibRefCitation>
from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[398,443,1520,1546]" name="Iran" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">Iran</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[497,642,1519,1545]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
and then reported also for 
<collectingCountry box="[944,1039,1519,1545]" name="Pakistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[1094,1162,1519,1545]" name="Oman" pageId="5" pageNumber="426">Oman</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Kubisz, D. &amp; Iwan, D." box="[1177,1333,1519,1545]" pageId="5" pageNumber="426" pagination="476 - 499" refId="ref6435" refString="Kubisz, D. &amp; Iwan, D. (2020) Family Oedemeridae. In: Iwan, D. &amp; Lobl, I. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 5. 2 nd Edition. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, pp. 476 - 499." type="book chapter" year="2020">Kubisz, 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
